snippet.textDisplay: She forgot to ask him why are more than 20 approved exemptions for other tennis players and whats the difference between Novak exception and the others?If he got approval from 2 different doctor panels and even ruled by a judge to stay to Australia, he was even granted a visa form before he came to Australia then based in which law does this decision is legitimate or which justification make it to be fair for Djokovic to leave if it is not for political reasons and the Covid thing.The whole meaning of this for me is the new world order we are living with the vaccination obligations..Its for All to understand its not about Novak but any of us that should have the right not to be vaccinated not put something in our body against our will and this is a great example to see whats going on behind the scenes but neither they tell us a lot of details..what was that Novak falcificated if he was approved from 2 different and legitimate Australian doctor panels?Not be allowed to go to lots of public places like malls plus super markets, bars - discotecks, restaurants, cafes, etc..seems like a discrimination between vaccinated and not vaccinated and this remind me the Apartheid end Nazi eras that was shame for humanity..if Novak Djokovic someone that has offer soo much to Australia (apart from winning 9 AO has also offer 25k for the fires) is treated like this imagine what could happen to any of us that is not vaccinated.Being treated like in China that is nothing like a democratic country.The vaccine hasn't been proven that is really working the opposite personally i have met people that got worst by doing the vaccine and others that died.There is not any logical justification for my point of view for such dictatoric measures and treatment when a probability for someone to die could be 0,001% for the vulnerables..considering that 9 to 10 are asymptomatic is ridiculous to forget human and fair treatment respect for decision of anyone not want to do the vaccine and especially for someone like Djokovic.The situation for me should really worry us for what is coming..i have taken Ivermectina a medicine between others that helps to kill the virus and lots of private doctors are recommended it and lots of people have helped but the government's and public help officials wont recommend any..weird..
